---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';

const seo = {
  title: `Core Board with Image Upload and Keyword Prediction | OS-DPI`,
  description: `ASL core board demonstration with AI plug-in for keyword prediction. Upload images and get related keyword predictions dynamically generated by AI.`,
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <TextSection narrow>
    <h1>Core Board with Image Upload and Keyword Prediction</h1>

    <p>The purpose of this demonstration UI is to demonstrate an example of an ASL core board with an AI plug-in for keyword prediction. You can download the file here: <a href="https://github.com/user-attachments/files/24946326/grid_ex_image_keyword_prediction.zip">grid_ex_image_keyword_prediction.zip</a></p>

    <p>Step-by-step instructions are available for plugging in the AI feature on your board.</p>

    <p><strong>Note:</strong> In the demo, you can switch between the developer mode and full-screen user-interface pressing the <kbd>Alt</kbd> or <kbd>Option</kbd> key followed by the <kbd>D</kbd> key.</p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Core word board</li>
      <li>Upload images</li>
      <li>Related keyword prediction for the image</li>
      <li>Prediction data is dynamically generated by an AI plug-in and can be trained or expanded based on user needs</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Interactive Demo</h2>
    <iframe
      src="https://unc-project-open-aac.github.io/OS-DPI/?fetch=https://github.com/user-attachments/files/24946326/grid_ex_image_keyword_prediction.zip"
      width="100%"
      height="600"
      style="border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 8px;"
      title="Interactive Demo"
    ></iframe>
  </TextSection>
</Layout>
